[SN]TITLE[SN]
Brian the dog helps 'reluctant readers' at Leigh school

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A primary school in Greater Manchester has a "novel" way to encourage students who are "reluctant readers".

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
11 March 2017 Last updated at 11:02 GMT
Leigh St Mary's Primary School has introduced the idea of children reading to a dog.
It's thought Books with Brian boosts the children's confidence as he listens without judging.
